				<div id="articleFull" class="articleFull"><p><span class="articleBegin">S</span>o the federal government is spending a bunch of money to get us to, as The Boston Globe-Democrat puts it, &ldquo;respect the legal drinking age of 21.&rdquo;</p>
<p>Good luck with that.</p>

